claude# Blu Markets v9.3 ‚Äî UI Refinement Changelog

## Overview

Implement 12 UI refinements focused on the onboarding experience and History tab. These changes improve clarity, user understanding, and overall delight.

**Important:** All UI text must be in English. The ONLY exceptions are:
- Questionnaire questions and answer options (during onboarding)
- The consent sentence that users must type

---

