## Issue 7: History ‚Äî Add Amounts to All Monetary Entries

**Current:** Some entries missing amounts (Loan Repaid, Funds Added, Borrowed, Protected).

**Change:** All monetary entries show amounts.

**Implementation:**

```jsx
const formatHistoryEntry = (entry) => {
  switch (entry.type) {
    case 'TRADE':
      const isBuy = entry.side === 'BUY';
      return {
        icon: isBuy ? '+' : '-',
        iconClass: isBuy ? 'trade-buy' : 'trade-sell',
        text: `${isBuy ? 'Bought' : 'Sold'} ${entry.assetName}`,
        amount: entry.amountIRR,
      };
    case 'LOAN_REPAID':
      return {
        icon: '‚úì',
        iconClass: 'action-success',
        text: 'Loan Repaid',
        amount: entry.amountIRR,  // ADD AMOUNT
      };
    case 'FUNDS_ADDED':
      return {
        icon: '+',
        iconClass: 'funds-add',
        text: 'Funds Added',
        amount: entry.amountIRR,  // ADD AMOUNT
      };
    case 'BORROWED':
      return {
        icon: 'üí∞',
        iconClass: 'action-loan',
        text: `Borrowed ${formatIRRShort(entry.amountIRR)} IRR against ${entry.collateralAsset}`,
        amount: entry.amountIRR,  // ADD AMOUNT
      };
    case 'PROTECTED':
      return {
        icon: '‚òÇÔ∏è',
        iconClass: 'action-protect',
        text: `Protected ${entry.assetName} (${entry.durationMonths}mo)`,
        amount: entry.premiumPaid,  // ADD PREMIUM
        amountLabel: 'Premium',
      };
    case 'REBALANCED':
      return {
        icon: '‚öñÔ∏è',
        iconClass: 'action-rebalance',
        text: 'Rebalanced',
        amount: null,  // No amount for rebalance
      };
    default:
      return { icon: '‚Ä¢', text: entry.type, amount: null };
  }
};
```

