## Issue 10: Left Panel vs History Tab ‚Äî Clear Purpose

**Current:** Both show similar information redundantly.

**Change:** Differentiate purpose:
- Left panel = Recent activity feed (last ~10 actions)
- History tab = Full searchable/filterable archive

**Implementation:**

Left panel (Action Log) ‚Äî limit to recent items:

```jsx
const ActionLog = ({ history }) => {
  const recentActions = history.slice(0, 10);  // Only last 10
  
  return (
    <div className="action-log">
      {recentActions.length === 0 ? (
        <div className="action-log-empty">No actions yet</div>
      ) : (
        recentActions.map((entry, i) => (
          <div key={i} className="action-log-entry">
            <span className="action-time">{formatTimeShort(entry.timestamp)}</span>
            <span className="action-text">{formatActionLogEntry(entry)}</span>
          </div>
        ))
      )}
    </div>
  );
};

// Compact format for left panel
const formatActionLogEntry = (entry) => {
  switch (entry.type) {
    case 'TRADE':
      return `${entry.side === 'BUY' ? '+' : '-'}${entry.assetName} ${formatIRRShort(entry.amountIRR)}`;
    case 'REBALANCED':
      return '‚öñÔ∏è Rebalanced';
    case 'BORROWED':
      return `üí∞ Borrowed ${formatIRRShort(entry.amountIRR)} against ${entry.collateralAsset}`;
    case 'PROTECTED':
      return `‚òÇÔ∏è ${entry.assetName} protected ${entry.durationMonths}mo`;
    // ... etc
  }
};
```

History tab ‚Äî full details with filtering (future enhancement):

```jsx
const HistoryTab = ({ history }) => {
  // Full history, grouped by date
  return (
    <div className="history-tab">
      {/* Future: Add search/filter controls here */}
      <HistoryList entries={history} />
